title: CCSD BOE Meeting to be at Worthington Elementary (Chillicothe City School District)
text: ( Source : Chillicothe City School District ) The Chillicothe Board of Education will meet on Monday, October 26th at Worthington Elementary . Please plan to attend! AGENDA - SUMMARY I. Call to Order President II. Roll Call Treasurer III .
